<Layout
  title="How to Build a News App with MobiLoud's News App Builder"
  description="Learn how to create a news app as good as The New York Times or BuzzFeed - in just weeks - with MobiLoud. Boost your engagement & revenue!"
>
  <Nav />

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 px-4">
